Name: OUTSP4CE
About the game: We are trying to protect our tiny planet from external threats. Our tiny green triangle tries to destroy enemies in the shape of red circles that are approaching our world by shooting them. Destroy enemies without forgetting about gravity and hitting the red circles. You will earn points for every red circle you destroy. Save the planet. Buttons: Space = Fire You can move left and right with the arrow keys.
